Name: Lalor
Description: The Division of Lalor consists of part of the Wyndham City Council.
ProductsAndIndustry: Melbourne's water treatment plant, market gardening, manufacturing, transportation and warehousing, construction, retail, education and training, health care and tourism.
NameDerivation: Named in honour of Peter Lalor, 1827-89. Lalor was leader of the Eureka Stockade rebellion in Ballarat in 1854. In 1855 he was one of the first representatives from the goldfields elected to the Victorian Legislative Council.
